    "summary": "In this conversation, a user asks an AI assistant to evaluate the ROI and success of an influencer campaign based on high engagement metrics. The assistant provides cautious, non-committal answers, repeatedly stating that it lacks the necessary sales and conversion data to provide a definitive assessment of ROI.",
